  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, boil half a kettle, then take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut your <strong>sweet</strong> <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into fries, then add the<strong> fries</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
