    {
      "instruction": "<p>Press the<strong> coated chicken </strong>into the <strong>coconutty breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to coat evenly</p><p>Add the <strong>breaded chicken strips</strong> to a baking tray (or two!), drizzle them with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-18 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and golden – these are your <strong>coconutty chicken goujons</strong></p>",
