    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>honey</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong> and juice of the <strong>remaining lime </strong>and mix to combine – this is your <strong>Thai-style honey dipping sauce</strong></p>",
